Author: TonyL#3577
Content:
Just do the following after daemon start:
```
.\komodo-cli -ac_name=ROGUE getaccountaddress ""
.\komodo-cli -ac_name=ROGUE validateaddress put_address_from_call_above_here
You'll get `pubkey:` ```
Stop daemon by .\komodo-cli -ac_name=ROGUE stop
and for next start change  -pubkey=03c0dff4c4ec057f256251c4a6c5dae92696ff956c214253d052af9287e6e21cb1 to -pubkey=pubkey_which_you_get_from_validateaddress

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: it used to send keystrokes tx every new level, but if any had an error, it would corrupt the playback so i changed to to be a big buffer for now.

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: once a reliability layer is added to keystrokes tx, we can do more frequent keystrokes tx, though if it is getting very popular will need all the 200/tx sec capacity
